										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>記者 陳聖偉 / 報導</p>



<blockquote class="wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow">
<p><strong>台灣本土創新再傳捷報。由 麥易購股份有限公司 研發推出的「遇見未來酒箱」，以獨家 「轉換結構容器」發明專利 與精密工藝設計，成功打破傳統陳釀的時間侷限，讓紅酒、威士忌、白酒與珍藏佳釀，在開啟之前展現更具層次與故事感的風味。</strong></p>
</blockquote>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1220" height="735" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/image-234.png?resize=1220%2C735&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-244873" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/image-234.png?w=2106&amp;ssl=1 2106w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/image-234.png?resize=768%2C463&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/image-234.png?resize=1536%2C926&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/image-234.png?resize=2048%2C1234&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/image-234.png?resize=780%2C470&amp;ssl=1 780w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/image-234.png?resize=242%2C146&amp;ssl=1 242w" sizes="(max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">台灣創新專利驚豔國際。圖片來源: 麥易購</figcaption></figure>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>科技工藝 × 美學體驗</strong></h2>



<p>「遇見未來酒箱」全程無需電力，純粹依靠科學工藝，即能保留酒品原有的風格，同時帶來品味升華的感官體驗。每一次舉杯，不僅是品飲，更是一場跨越時間的風味旅程。</p>



<p>酒箱本體採用布藝包覆與木製盒體，溫潤手感結合藝術收藏價值，展現台灣設計的細膩與精緻。</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>專屬認證 × 尊榮收藏</strong></h2>



<p>為確保真品獨特性，每一只酒箱皆配備 防偽碼與隱藏式 NFC 掃描，建立專屬真品認證機制，提升收藏與贈禮價值，成為高端市場的尊榮之選。</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1220" height="610" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/messageImage_1755507711257_0-scaled.jpg?resize=1220%2C610&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-244740" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/messageImage_1755507711257_0-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/messageImage_1755507711257_0-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C384&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/messageImage_1755507711257_0-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C768&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/messageImage_1755507711257_0-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/messageImage_1755507711257_0-scaled.jpg?resize=260%2C130&amp;ssl=1 260w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/messageImage_1755507711257_0-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">酒箱本體採用布藝包覆與木製盒體，溫潤手感結合藝術收藏價值，展現台灣設計的細膩與精緻。圖片來源: 麥易購</figcaption></figure>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>外銷接單持續成長</strong></h2>



<p>自產品亮相以來，外銷訂單需求持續攀升，展現國際市場對台灣創新設計的高度肯定。麥易購表示，未來將積極拓展亞洲及歐美市場，讓更多消費者體驗「跨越時間的美學品味」。</p>



<p>產品資訊</p>



<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; •&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 保固：一年（非人為損壞）</p>



<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; •&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 外尺寸：10 × 10 × 34.5 cm</p>



<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; •&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 內尺寸：10 × 8 × 33 cm</p>



<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; •&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 重量：842.5 g</p>



<p>遇見未來，不只是酒，更是一場時光與美學交織的體驗。</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1220" height="610" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/messageImage_1755507713350_0-scaled.jpg?resize=1220%2C610&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-244741" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/messageImage_1755507713350_0-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/messageImage_1755507713350_0-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C384&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/messageImage_1755507713350_0-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C768&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/messageImage_1755507713350_0-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/messageImage_1755507713350_0-scaled.jpg?resize=260%2C130&amp;ssl=1 260w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/messageImage_1755507713350_0-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">「遇見未來酒箱」開啟跨越時光的風味旅程。圖片來源: 麥易購</figcaption></figure>



